{"tid":1221463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸：修例稍為延遲也不壞　林健鋒：政府解說不足","createTime":"2019-06-14T08:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T10:35:06.000Z","uid":132998,"like":13,"dislike":551,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"075ed04125a286e9ef0bdfe8c2eb53d7ddf11857","tid":1221463,"uid":132998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:14:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462876.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462876.htm&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpK9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=72d61557\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462876.htm&h=0cf54171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462876.htm</a><br />\n2019-06-14 HKT 16:07<br />\n立法會連續3日暫停大會會議，未能恢復二讀辯論修訂《逃犯條例》草案，亦引發日前金鐘的大規模示威。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸認為，政府一再修改草案，現只剩犯重大罪案人士才會引渡，因此不需撤回修例。但她認為，修例稍為延遲也不壞，然後政府應檢討，為何無威脅的條例會引致市民如此大反彈，質疑是政府宣傳不足，望政府可趁空檔多宣傳解釋。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯的林健鋒認為，政府解說確有不足，雖然政府修補法例漏洞出發點好，但從不少媒體可看到市民不明白修例，他自己亦多次向不明白的商界人士解釋，至於會議安排，則需留待政府與立法會主席梁君彥商討。"},{"pid":"2ce59c3961798f03ae16b7541f69eb1260d7503f","tid":1221463,"uid":9541,"like":598,"dislike":1,"score":597,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:15:38.000Z","msg":"班傻西放好多錢係美國咩？<br />\n淆底呀？"},{"pid":"d45c0dcd87f3bd6cc765d817dca899ab1f586118","tid":1221463,"uid":104804,"like":294,"dislike":0,"score":294,"quote":{"pid":"2ce59c3961798f03ae16b7541f69eb1260d7503f","tid":1221463,"uid":9541,"like":598,"dislike":1,"score":597,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:15:38.000Z","msg":"班傻西放好多錢係美國咩？<br />\n淆底呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:16:17.000Z","msg":"仔女呀"},{"pid":"4ffa4fb4a59228acb96d9a4fc8fd29dc73a671bf","tid":1221463,"uid":12412,"like":157,"dislike":2,"score":155,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T08:16:19.000Z","msg":"延你老母"},{"pid":"5c736266f3c13c24e58de60aedade8dec773df57","tid":1221463,"uid":33868,"like":377,"dislike":0,"s