msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姐係絕對唔可以俾政府拖</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a400f669b98e05f1c436c0134b9e718f3b6185a5","tid":1221463,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:09:49.000Z","msg":"媽呀 點解會咁架<br />\n老老柒柒 我真係預佢會過<br />\n<strong>我好想睇你班賤人比侵侵抄家回血</strong><br />\n你地轉得咁快 我D花生點食呀...."},{"pid":"0e534fc2c7ac163103c5bde6eb558b5b6fa0b6de","tid":1221463,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"割得咁快<br />\n美國好多資產？"},{"pid":"5bb711d0814ca61f2cf60f68f8c4ee087a459c58","tid":1221463,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:10:11.000Z","msg":"仆街啦你<br />\n不撤不退"},{"pid":"0ed94056c51f358395eb54aebc13fe7781c00af2","tid":1221463,"uid":35452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T09:12:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭化系,大難臨頭果然各自飛,好撚肉9 酸"}]}